I want to THANK whoever came up with this idea.
Now, what makes this place "the new lounge" to be in is its location.
Found inside the gorgeous Bellagio, right in the center of it all facing the Bellagio Fountains.
If you are on a budget this might be a bit expensive but it's definitely a place to check out.
Oh, I still want to find out who is that girl behind the mask, I'm intrigued!
